c Presentation]]\n| Anna Boden & Ryan Fleck & Geneva Robertson-Dworet \n| {{pending}}\n|scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"NebulaAward\" />\n|}\n\n== Sequel ==\n{{further|List of Marvel Cinematic Universe films#Untitled Captain Marvel sequel _(2022)}}\n\nIn February 2019, Larson expressed interest in including the character [[Ms. Marvel (Kamala Khan)|Kamala Khan / Ms. Marvel]] in a sequel;<ref name=\"MsMarvel\" /> Feige previously said he had plans to introduce Khan to the MCU following the release of ''Captain Marvel''.<ref name=\"MsMarvel2\" /> The following month, Feige said he had \"pretty amazing\" ideas for a ''Captain Marvel'' sequel.<ref name=\"FeigeSequel\" /> Feige added that a possible sequel could explore the time gap between the end of this film and Danvers' next appearance in ''[[Avengers: Endgame]]''.<ref name=\"FeigeSequel2\" /> [[Lashana Lynch]] expressed interest in reprising her role as Maria Rambeau in such a sequel.<ref name=\"LynchSequel\" /> Feige confirmed the film is in development at the 2019 San Diego Comic-Con.<ref name=\"SDCC\" /> In January 2020, Megan McDonnell was in final negotiations to write the script for the film. Fleck and Boden were not expected to return to direct the film, with the studio searching instead for a female director. The sequel would take place in the present day,<ref name=\"McDonnellSequel\" /> and is scheduled to be released on July 8, 2022.<ref name=\"Phase4Delay\" />\n\n== Notes ==\n{{Reflist|group=N}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"Runtime\">{{Citation|url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/captain-marvel-2019|title=Captain Marvel|publisher=[[British Board of Film Classification]]|access-date=March 5, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190304132542/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/captain-marvel-2019|archive-date=March 4, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BOM\">{{Cite web|title=Captain Marvel (2019)|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=marvel2018a.htm|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|access-date=July 27, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714095612/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=marvel2018a.htm|archive-date=July 14, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CaptainMarvel\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/will-captain-marvel-play-wild-avengers-infinity-war-ending/|title=How Will 'Captain Marvel' Play into That Wild 'Avengers: Infinity War' Ending?|last1=Hornshaw|first1=Phil|last2=Owen|first2=Phil|last3=Lincoln|first3=Ross A.|website=[[TheWrap]]|date=April 26, 2018|access-date=March 7, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427030538/https://www.thewrap.com/will-captain-marvel-play-wild-avengers-infinity-war-ending/|archive-date=April 27, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"THRMay2013\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/marvel-cliffhanger-robert-downey-jrs-518837|title=Marvel Cliffhanger: Robert Downey Jr.'s $50 Million Sequel Showdown|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|last2=Bond|first2=Paul|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=May 7, 2013|access-date=May 8, 2013|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ny75kG8k?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/marvel-cliffhanger-robert-downey-jrs-518837|archive-date=March 10, 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ComingSoonSep2013\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=108585|title=Marvel Studios Wants a Female-Led Superhero Film|last=Lesnick|first=Silas|website=[[ComingSoon.net]]|date=September 5, 2013|access-date=August 29, 2014|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SBmigSfa?url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=108585|archive-date=August 29, 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BadassDigestMarch2014\">{{Cite web|url=http://badassdigest.com/2014/03/14/kevin-feige-on-marvels-responsibility-to-be-diverse-and-a-possible-captain|title=Kevin Feige on Marvel's Responsibility To Be Diverse and a Possible Captain Marvel Movie|last=Faraci|first=Dev